body_html:
An update for those interested
I've managed to get past the compiling problems of protoc. I managed to get past the linker error by adding -lm in 'google/protobuf/BUILD'.

However, now I managed to get an actual compiling error, similar to the one mentioned here: #439
I'll monitor the other issue and see if a solution for that ticket can be applied to my problem as well.
